title: Housekeeping
description:
Swagu and Perk address the latest setback for Zion Williamson, how Steph Curry is held to a different standard than LeBron James, Dak Prescott's dip in performance, the Urban Meyer debacle in Jacksonville, and how they approach gift giving for the holidays. Let's get it.
